    "description": "<strong>《启示录：哈里的世界末日》</strong>是一款沿着《银河历险记》及《机械迷城》的脉络而制作的传统指点式冒险游戏，游戏里的所有谜团都有隐藏的意义。游戏画风深受15世纪雕刻艺术所启发，讲述了一个充满心碎与救赎、如世界末日一般的故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/2d2478d92ecbbead08e4ea3fc572b494.poster.avif?t=1752773469\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/2d2478d92ecbbead08e4ea3fc572b494.webm?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/2d2478d92ecbbead08e4ea3fc572b494.mp4?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>在《启示录》里，你就是主人公哈里，对于他来说，失去了挚爱就像陷入了世界末日一样痛苦。现在他必须踏上那片陌生又冷清的土地寻找他挚爱的女孩。旅途中，他会碰到各种出自中世纪欧洲艺术家头脑的神奇生物，并最终征服他内心的恶魔。</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/62f95373d0300ac2d87f65909c73778e.poster.avif?t=1752773469\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/62f95373d0300ac2d87f65909c73778e.webm?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/62f95373d0300ac2d87f65909c73778e.mp4?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《启示录》有着中世纪的艺术风格，游戏里的世界来源于《圣约翰启示录》，并融合了中世纪的哲学和信仰。同时，故事也借鉴了但丁的《神曲》。<br>《启示录》里的每个角色和场景都深受中世纪版画艺术启发，借鉴了包括小汉斯·霍尔拜因、瓦格莫特及阿尔布雷斯特·丢勒在内等15、16世纪画家创作的古典版画。<strong>中世纪艺术与电子游戏的结合为玩家打造了前所未见的独特风格。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在《启示录》里，你可以：</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><i>体验情节跌宕起伏的经典指点式冒险类游戏</i></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/8a553da0a8b1dc01ca80888ec4b02b08.poster.avif?t=1752773469\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/8a553da0a8b1dc01ca80888ec4b02b08.webm?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/8a553da0a8b1dc01ca80888ec4b02b08.mp4?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong><i>见证中世纪艺术在电子游戏中重生</i></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/c30b968ce966715680b59a14f3253abf.poster.avif?t=1752773469\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/c30b968ce966715680b59a14f3253abf.webm?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/c30b968ce966715680b59a14f3253abf.mp4?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><i><strong>看到15世纪古书记载的神奇生物</strong></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/2b17df8873cd0fdef61e669b5fb7ed7c.poster.avif?t=1752773469\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/2b17df8873cd0fdef61e669b5fb7ed7c.webm?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/2b17df8873cd0fdef61e669b5fb7ed7c.mp4?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong><i>踏上如同末日的旅程，感受可能的其中一种结局</i></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/b131df7d27506ade23397f699d4cc46f.poster.avif?t=1752773469\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/b131df7d27506ade23397f699d4cc46f.webm?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/b131df7d27506ade23397f699d4cc46f.mp4?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong><i>在二十多个设有大量神秘谜团的场景里冒险，找出谜团背后的深意</i></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/b5250f84c49d0b4ffc5ce745b32f0125.poster.avif?t=1752773469\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/b5250f84c49d0b4ffc5ce745b32f0125.webm?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/b5250f84c49d0b4ffc5ce745b32f0125.mp4?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>像1495年时期的那些伟人一样，获得自己的成就!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/cc590964ade5b55e32da2c29f35d0b25.poster.avif?t=1752773469\" width=610 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/cc590964ade5b55e32da2c29f35d0b25.webm?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/505330/extras/cc590964ade5b55e32da2c29f35d0b25.mp4?t=1752773469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
